A Day in the Life of Product & Engineering



















        							Maggie's Day
        							





 







Morning

Product managers prep demos for Science Fair. But first, espresso.
UX researchers hop on the first customer user test of the day. 

Mid-Afternoon

Tech Talk time: The platform team is talking about updates to our tech stack.
Designers mock up new dashboard styles inspired by a team workshop.

Afternoon

An engineer on the Website Grader team merges pull requests, tests on QA, and deploys to production.
Everyone gets their game faces on at the Instagram Scavenger Hunt. 

















