HubSpot, Inc.

25 First Street, 2nd Floor 
Cambridge MA 02141 United States
Phone: +1 857-___-____
Fax: +1 617-___-____
http://www.hubspot.com





67
Managers




30
IT employees




$6.9MEST.
IT Budget




HubSpot, Inc.is a marketing software solutions company. The company offers inbound marketing tools, mail marketing software, search engine optimization, business blogging, competitor analysis, and closed-loop marketing analytics
Hubspot, Inc.'s IT department operates out of the company's Cambridge, MA, location. The executive who is in charge of internal IT also manages product research and development and product infrastructure operations.

The IT staff is responsible for employees' computers, telecommunications, hardware,… MoreHubspot, Inc.'s IT department operates out of the company's Cambridge, MA, location. The executive who is in charge of internal IT also manages product research and development and product infrastructure operations.

The IT staff is responsible for employees' computers, telecommunications, hardware, logins, and email accounts. An IT lead works with managers within the organization to determine what equipment and/or resources will be required for company growth and handles contracts and negotiations with vendors.

The company's SaaS products use MySQL databases. The staff primarily uses CentOS and RHEL for database tuning and administration.





